data.description: This home is truly a gem! As you enter the home you are welcomed into a spacious family room that leads into an open kitchen with a breakfast area that offers views of the back patio and yard, where you can sit and enjoy your morning coffee. The interior, which has 3 br and 2.5 baths, has been updated with freshly painted cabinets and new floors. The master bedroom boasts a soaking tub and shower. The secondary bedrooms are spacious with walk in closets. There is plenty of room and opportunity to grow and make it yours! Won't last long.
